PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FA man who denies a brutal rape for
OL,7,Fwhich an innocent man spent 17 years
OL,8,Fin jail has told a jury he does not
OL,9,Fknow how his DNA got on the victim's
OL,10,Fclothes.
OL,12,FPaul Quinn, 51, agreed it was his DNA
OL,13,Fon the woman's vest top, which was
OL,14,Fonly recovered years later after
OL,15,Fpolice were able to re-test a sample
OL,16,Fusing better techniques which came
OL,17,Fback as a billion-to-one match of his
OL,18,FDNA profile.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FBy then, Andrew Malkinson had already
OL,7,Fbeen convicted and jailed for the rape
OL,8,Fin 2003.
OL,10,FAsked to explain why he had been
OL,11,Fsearching on the internet for how long
OL,12,Fpolice keep DNA samples, Quinn
OL,13,Freplied: "Just inquisitiveness," the
OL,14,Fjury at Manchester Crown Court was
OL,15,Ftold.
OL,17,FFather-of-six Quinn denies any
OL,18,Finvolvement in the attack on July 19,
OL,19,F2003 on Cleggs Lane, Little Hulton,
OL,20,FSalford.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FMr Malkinson, working as a security
OL,7,Fguard at a shopping centre, was the
OL,8,Fvictim of a terrible miscarriage of
OL,9,Fjustice, the trial has heard.
OL,11,FNo DNA evidence linked him to the
OL,12,Fcrime but he had been wrongly picked
OL,13,Fout at an identity parade and later
OL,14,Fconvicted and jailed, spending 17
OL,15,Fyears behind bars.
OL,17,FThe DNA sample from the vest top had
OL,18,Fbeen identified in 2007, and analysis
OL,19,Fhad ruled out any link to Mr Malkinson.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FThe sample was identified as coming
OL,7,Ffrom "Unknown Male 1", but it was not
OL,8,Funtil 2022 that police matched it to
OL,9,Fthe defendant, who had given police a
OL,10,Fsample of his own DNA in 2012.
OL,12,FLisa Wilding KC, defending Quinn, who
OL,13,Fwas giving evidence from the witness
OL,14,Fbox, asked him: "Do you accept it's
OL,15,Fyour DNA on the victim's vest top?"
OL,17,F"I do, yes," replied Quinn.
OL,19,FMs Wilding continued: "Do you know how
OL,20,Fit got there?"
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@UO]vD@QOUwD@cO]yD@AOUyD@LO]{D@
OL,26,AWOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,F"I do not know," the defendant replied.
OL,8,FMs Wilding said: "Mr Quinn, did it get
OL,9,Fthere because you raped and attacked
OL,10,Fher on that night?"
OL,12,F"No," replied Quinn.
OL,14,FThe victim, a mother-of-two in her
OL,15,F30s, was dragged from the street
OL,16,Fbeside a motorway embankment, brutally
OL,17,Fbeaten, with a nipple almost severed
OL,18,Fand her cheekbone fractured, and
OL,19,Fstrangled unconscious before being
OL,20,Fraped twice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@PO]pD@ROUrD@SO]tD@AOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial, Quinn was
OL,7,Faccused of trying to explain away the
OL,8,FDNA evidence by claiming to have led a
OL,9,Fhighly promiscuous party lifestyle,
OL,10,Fsleeping with hundreds or even
OL,11,Fthousands of local women.
OL,13,FQuinn, who worked as a fencing
OL,14,Fcontractor, was asked about police
OL,15,Fevidence of his internet use,
OL,16,Fincluding websites visited and Google
OL,17,Fsearches on his iPhone, recovered
OL,18,Fafter his arrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FHe was asked about one search using
OL,7,Fthe term "Wrongly convicted cases in
OL,8,Fthe UK".
OL,10,FQuinn said: "I have always shown an
OL,11,Finterest in crime programmes,
OL,12,Fsomething I have always enjoyed
OL,13,Fwatching. Like true crime."
OL,15,FHe was then asked why in August 2022
OL,16,Fhe had searched for "How long is DNA
OL,17,Fkept in database".
OL,19,FQuinn said: "It was just to satisfy
OL,20,Fquestions I had in my own head. Just
OL,21,Finquisitiveness."
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@GO]rD@MOUuD@[O]xD@UOUyD@QO]{D@
OL,26,AMOU}D@QO]
