FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FMr Malkinson made multiple appeals for
OL,7,Fauthorities to review his case before
OL,8,Fhis final attempt led to his appeal
OL,9,Fagainst his conviction being granted
OL,10,Fby the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FNow aged 60, and originally from
OL,13,FGrimsby, Lincolnshire, he was released
OL,14,Ffrom jail in 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FQuinn, who moved from Little Hulton to
OL,7,FExeter, Devon, in 2017, after he
OL,8,Fseparated and was divorced from his
OL,9,Fwife, has pleaded not guilty to two
OL,10,Fcounts of rape, two alternative counts
OL,11,Fof indecent assault, grievous bodily
OL,12,Fharm and attempting to choke or
OL,13,Fstrangle his victim to render her
OL,14,Funconscious while he carried out the
OL,15,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FDuring cross-examination, prosecutor
OL,7,FJohn Price KC suggested internet
OL,8,Fsearches by Quinn in 2019 showed he
OL,9,Flooked up the case of Mr Malkinson
OL,10,Fbefore the campaign against his
OL,11,Fwrongful conviction had hit the
OL,12,Fheadlines.
OL,14,FMr Price said: "It looks, Mr Quinn, as
OL,15,Fthough you knew that might be a
OL,16,Fwrongful conviction long before
OL,17,Fanybody else. It seems like that way."
OL,19,FQuinn replied: "Yes, but it's not that
OL,20,Fway, it may seem so."
OL,26,@vD@POUyD@fO]{D@POU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774598700
OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FMr Price continued: "Well, I'm going
OL,7,Fto suggest that the explanation is, in
OL,8,FSeptember 2019, there were two people
OL,9,Fwho knew Mr Malkinson's was a wrongful
OL,10,Fconviction. Him and you. Is that the
OL,11,Ftruth?"
OL,13,F"No," Quinn replied.
OL,15,FMr Price said: "And you knew that his
OL,16,Fwas a wrongful conviction, because you
OL,17,Fknew the person who attacked the
OL,18,Fvictim was you?"
OL,20,F"No," Quinn again replied.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@GO]uD@AOUuD@EO]wD@POUzD@PO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@EO]
