OL,3,CRape accused 'cannot explain DNA on
OL,4,Cvictim's clothes'
OL,6,FThe trial was adjourned until Friday
OL,7,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
